(Thanks Nenelar, Sayleth, Wabbus,Taji, Graffe's and Necro Boards, and to all you guys that are helping figure this out <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->                     )<br>
